5: Oh, found you guys! Alk! Stella!
13:
Hey. Dropping by for a change of
pace?
23: Um... Hello. It's nice to see you again.
31:
I came today because there's
something I wanted to discuss...
36:
...So you want to run in different
places and take in new sights as a
change of pace?
40:
Yes. I've more or less seen
everything around the academy...
44:
Suzuka's amazing! She does her own
training runs every day before and
after school!
48:
I tried tagging along once, and she
had us running until curfew!
53:
I-It's not like I'm the only one working
hard... I know you practice a lot too,
Spe.
58:
But not the way you do! I think you're
the only one I know who trains with
such a happy look on your face!
63:
If you ask me, you're both something
else...
68:
This is why Air Groove—um, a friend
of ours—is always worried and
scolding me.
73:
Hehe, you and her are close friends!
It's only natural, right?
78:
Suzuka, you really love running, don't
you?
84: I do. I love it so, so much.
89:
The other day, she had a dream
where she was running on clouds in
the sky and ended up falling out of
bed!
94:
S-Spe, you don't have to tell them
that!
99:
Even in your dreams, you're running
in new places, huh?
103:
I-I thought that since I have the
opportunity to now, I should see the
views that other worlds have to
offer...
106:
I want to run anywhere and
everywhere. Back home, that usually
just means the mountains, but I'm
sure I can handle more than that.
110:
You ran through mountains?!
That's... impressive... In that case...
113:
Y-you! You're Silence Suzuka, aren't
you?!
116:
Y-yes, I am. Excuse me, but who are
you?
119:
Ah, right, you wouldn't remember
since we never spoke directly.
121:
I'm a golem researcher at Voluntas
Academy. I worked on one of the
golems that you raced against.
123:
I've been looking all over for you,
hoping I could gather data on your
running form. Would you be willing
to join me on the racetrack one
more time?
129:
I can't believe how lucky I am to see
you run again!
132:
Um... Thank you for having me. I'll do
my best.
136: I wish I could run too...
139:
Actually, I was hoping I could record
your data after this! The more data,
the better!
142:
Are you sure you're okay with this? I
know you wanted to run somewhere
else, but...
146:
Honestly, I can't complain as long as
I'm able to run.
152:
Everything here is different from
what I'm used to. There's still
potential for me to see something
new as I go.
156:
I underestimated your love for
running... Good luck, then!
160:
Luck? I'm not sure what I need luck
for, but thank you.
164:
All right, let's get this show on the
road!
170: Okay... On your mark, get set... Go!
174:
There's so much energy in this
place, so much passion... I'm not
used to all of it...
177:
But that just means there's new
scenery for me to see.
188:
She's so fast... and she looks so
pretty while running.
192: That's the Suzuka I know and love!
199:
Phew, that felt great! Did you have
fun too, Suzuka?
203:
Yeah, that was a good change of
pace. Thanks for bringing me here,
Spe.
206:
...Um, I was wondering... Are there
other places with good scenery that
you know about?
210:
What kind of scenery are you
looking for?
214:
We've got places with forests, vast
plains... Even a desert, but that
might be hard to run in.
219:
A desert? That sounds interesting. It
must be very hot there...
224:
You better prep yourself so you don't
end up burnt to a crisp!
229:
I can't wait to take in all these
unexplored sights...
